reviewText: I liked this movie and it was cheap and the service was very fast
This picture is pretty. The Virgin Mary visit Mexico to unite people of all races. The love of God is always the center for that all things can be possible.
Movie was as well to be expected being that the movie is an older version.  Bought the movie as a gift for a family member.
This movie is the best you will ever get about La Virgen de la Guadalupe. It will make you cry, smile and put the story in a new perspective. a must have for every one.
